title: Coolidge Corner 2-Bed Condo With Garage Parking!
posting_body: ['Please call or email today :-)', 'Chris Masterman', 'of Unlimited Sotheby’s International Realty', '617-467-8198', 'Coolidge Corner 2-Bed Condo With Garage Parking!', 'Coolidge Corner', '$3200 /month', 'Features:', 'Located in a well managed Coolidge Corner condo building, this sunny and spacious two bedroom apartment is available for September 1st move-in!', 'Wood floors throughout most of the unit, modern kitchen (stainless steel appliances), and decorative fireplace.', 'Laundry is in the basement.', 'Minutes to T & bus lines, shopping, restaurants, and multiple parks.', 'One garage parking spot is included in the rent, as is heat and hot water!', "THIS LISTING IS EXCLUSIVE TO UNLIMITED SOTHEBY'S INTERNATIONAL REALTY", 'Please call or email today', 'Chris Masterman', 'of Unlimited Sotheby’s International Realty', '767 Beacon Street', 'Newton Centre, MA 02459', '617-467-8198']
